messageBody:
Uma Maheswara.G wrote:

> Thanks and it's correct ...i want to extract that particular time to
> result file , is there anyway of doing or coding with junit framework...

The Ant task <junit-report> would provide you with a report containing
that information. For more details, go to http://ant.apache.org
